cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.ST

The paper deals with clustering algorithms for big data, which is a common topic in machine learning and data science. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with data structures and algorithms, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The use of clustering algorithms in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) is also possible. Finally, the paper deals with real-time response and unknown data statistics, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.ST (Statistics).
